# Core Stack Rules

The stack for this project is locked. Never suggest alternatives.

- API layer: FastAPI only
- Task queue: Dramatiq + Redis broker only
- Database: PostgreSQL only
- ORM: SQLAlchemy async only
- Migrations: Alembic only
- Deployment: Docker Compose only
- Language: Python 3.11+
- SMS provider: MSG91 only (not Twilio)
- Email: SMTP only (no third-party email SDKs)

Never introduce new dependencies without an explicit instruction from the user.
Always check `docs/DECISIONS.md` before suggesting any architectural change.
